name: CRYPTO CLOUDS
description: CLOUD is the face of the crypto cloud. The project launched its vision in November 2021, making it one of the first memetokens on ICP. High liquidity on two different dapps and the arbitrage pools with different core assets on ICPSwap make us stand out (ICP, ckBTC, ckETH, SNS, SNEED). Many memes and an ever-growing community based on natural growth is our goal. CLOUD was added to the OpenChat wallet as the first major utility. We have good relations with the major projects and the ICP community.
